snippet.title: Quest of Dungeons Trailer
snippet.description:
Quest of Dungeons is a turn based dungeon crawler game, a roguelike.
An evil Dark Lord has stolen all the light, so your mission is to enter his lair and defeat him. Play as a Warrior, a Wizard, a Shaman or an Assassin to fight your way through the dungeon.

http://www.questofdungeons.com

Here's the first part of this video, the Story trailer http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=md0W9Lrn6fY
